  "text": "Serious injury reports by this cohort are slightly higher than that published after falls in older adults (5-10%) [CITATION_1] and previously reported in ambulant adults with CP [CITATION_2] . This adds to the growing body of evidence regarding falls in this population with unknown likely financial impact on health services and carers. Anecdotally, there is very limited emphasis on falls prevention education provided to adults with CP.",
